      <title>印度央行的债券购买将收益率推至三年来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/rbi-s-bond-purchases-push-india-yields-to-a-three-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示，印度央行大量购买债券以缓解现金短缺，此后印度主权债券收益率跌至近三年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/rbi-s-bond-purchases-push-india-yields-to-a-three-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 04:38:19 GMT</pubDate>
