      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 00:59:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的快速贸易行动扰乱市场，油价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对特朗普政府迅速采取的贸易举措作出反应，油价出现波动，美国先是威胁对哥伦比亚实施一系列限制措施，随后又推迟了这一决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 23:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 助力中国人工智能发展，亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市上涨，部分原因是对中国人工智能的乐观情绪，在最后一刻达成的协议推翻了唐纳德·特朗普对哥伦比亚征收关税的决定后，克服了市场普遍的谨慎情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 22:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普扰乱关税观点 债券交易员将焦点转向美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/bond-traders-shift-focus-to-fed-as-trump-shadows-the-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在债券市场，唐纳德·特朗普上任的第一周至少没有人们担心的那么不稳定。交易员们希望美联储的最新举措也能带来同样的效果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/bond-traders-shift-focus-to-fed-as-trump-shadows-the-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
